  "text": "Modelling the wound healing processes S. N. Menon et al. 3335 that we observe in the case of chronic hypoxia is also in agreement with the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Our model predicts that hypoxic wounds can be successfully treated with the application of supplemental oxygen, which is consistent with recent reviews [CITATION_3] .",
